---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Thinking Out Loud">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>Where these ideas come from</h1>

    <img src="/images/author.jpg" alt="Pablo Bañón" class="author-photo" />

    <p>
      This is a space for thoughts shared in long form, unfiltered and unedited.
      The videos are recorded in a single take — what you see is what was thought in that moment.
      This website is the written counterpart of those reflections.
    </p>

    <p>
      The idea is simple: thinking out loud, letting ideas flow just as they come,
      without polishing or disguising them. Sometimes they will be clear, sometimes messy — but always honest.
    </p>

    <p class="channel-link">
      You can watch the videos on the
      <a href="https://youtube.com/@pensandoenvozalta">YouTube channel</a>.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to home</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .author-photo {
    max-width: 280px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .channel-link {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>
